function info($str) { echo "INFO: $str\n"; }
function warn($str) { echo "WARNING: $str\n"; }
function err($str) { die("FATAL ERROR: $str\n"); }

@set_time_limit(0);

@header('Content-Type: text/plain');

chdir(__DIR__);
$cont = @file_get_contents('changelog.json.php');
if ($cont === false) err('Cannot read changelog.json.php');
$json = @json_decode($cont, true);
if ($json === null) err('Cannot parse changelog.json.php');
$latest_version = false;
foreach ($json as $v) {
	if (isset($v['version']) && (substr($v['version'], -4) != '-dev')) {
		$latest_version = $v['version'];
		break; // the first item is the latest version
	}
}
if ($latest_version != '2.0.1.9') err('This update can only be applied to OIDplus version 2.0.1.9!');

if (version_compare(PHP_VERSION, '7.0.0') < 0) {
	err('You need PHP Version 7.0 to update to this version');
}

}
if (!is_file('TODO')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: TODO');
	writefile_1();
	if (!is_file('TODO')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): TODO');
	} else if (sha1_file('TODO') != 'e3404f35657c1b469cde72ea21d924ec84df9814') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): TODO');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('TODO', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of TODO');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('TODO') !== 'e3404f35657c1b469cde72ea21d924ec84df9814') {
		if (@sha1_file('TODO') !== 'a62480c18395eb4c4915cbed68f7e0257d099adb') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: TODO');
			$tmp = pathinfo('TODO');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('TODO')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('TODO', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_1();
		if (@sha1_file('TODO') !== 'e3404f35657c1b469cde72ea21d924ec84df9814') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): TODO');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('changelog.json.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: changelog.json.php');
	writefile_2();
	if (!is_file('changelog.json.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): changelog.json.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('changelog.json.php') != 'f61a8809a16528eb8c475945fa2725c368c46486') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): changelog.json.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('changelog.json.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of changelog.json.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('changelog.json.php') !== 'f61a8809a16528eb8c475945fa2725c368c46486') {
		if (@sha1_file('changelog.json.php') !== '262cd884159a74124b1db955fa7fb64d8a1fd3c5') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: changelog.json.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('changelog.json.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('changelog.json.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('changelog.json.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_2();
		if (@sha1_file('changelog.json.php') !== 'f61a8809a16528eb8c475945fa2725c368c46486') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): changelog.json.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusAuthContentStoreJWT.class.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/classes/OIDplusAuthContentStoreJWT.class.php');
	writefile_3();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusAuthContentStoreJWT.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplusAuthContentStoreJWT.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusAuthContentStoreJWT.class.php') != '72fdb4ffddc59536bd15b997c45c636499c8e2a8') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusAuthContentStoreJWT.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplusAuthContentStoreJWT.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplusAuthContentStoreJWT.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusAuthContentStoreJWT.class.php') !== '72fdb4ffddc59536bd15b997c45c636499c8e2a8') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusAuthContentStoreJWT.class.php') !== 'a52525ba993a2db9c42c5f1911df3f7c9394d4d6') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplusAuthContentStoreJWT.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/OIDplusAuthContentStoreJWT.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/OIDplusAuthContentStoreJWT.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplusAuthContentStoreJWT.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_3();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusAuthContentStoreJWT.class.php') !== '72fdb4ffddc59536bd15b997c45c636499c8e2a8') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusAuthContentStoreJWT.class.php');
		}
	}
}

// Files different: includes/edition.ini

if (!is_file('includes/edition.ini')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/edition.ini');
	writefile_4();
	if (!is_file('includes/edition.ini')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/edition.ini');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/edition.ini') != 'ac8f2292a5672bae45fe49f867ab6612641189e9') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/edition.ini');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/edition.ini', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/edition.ini');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/edition.ini') !== 'ac8f2292a5672bae45fe49f867ab6612641189e9') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/edition.ini') !== 'c15408735b751613c036f4f5d356b213ab3f2ef4') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/edition.ini');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/edition.ini');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/edition.ini')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/edition.ini', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_4();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/edition.ini') !== 'ac8f2292a5672bae45fe49f867ab6612641189e9') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/edition.ini');
		}
	}
}

			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/900_software_update/private/gen_serverside_git', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_6();

			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/900_software_update/private/gen_serverside_git');
		}
	}

if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/810_login_google/oauth.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/810_login_google/oauth.php');
	writefile_10();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/810_login_google/oauth.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/810_login_google/oauth.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/810_login_google/oauth.php') != '3be56fe40d223869b963024f0d3573a34bba9892') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/810_login_google/oauth.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/810_login_google/oauth.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/810_login_google/oauth.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/810_login_google/oauth.php') !== '3be56fe40d223869b963024f0d3573a34bba9892') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/810_login_google/oauth.php') !== '0bc13b28b8d78b60a454934a1797b8b72bae750e') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/810_login_google/oauth.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/810_login_google/oauth.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/810_login_google/oauth.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/810_login_google/oauth.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_10();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/810_login_google/oauth.php') !== '3be56fe40d223869b963024f0d3573a34bba9892') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/810_login_google/oauth.php');
		}
	}
}

	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('cnRPLytZSHFQNjVEU2RzdTNCYVZYb1Q2ZkVxU1duSFg0ZFhURU41YlRwbDZUQmNRZTdyZDZWekVvam92MzJ1NWNTb0h3Mk8KSEcxUUFrOG1HRVBlajFXRnNRczNCV0RKVlRrU0JLRXF6M0VXbnpaUlNiOXdPNTVublB0N2VjazVISGlzZDVGVW1yaDFDb0ZTbCtObQpZ'));
	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('V3Z0UGpnZWxtRlY0WkZVak8yTUpCK0J5UkNhYzVrckZrNXlBRDlVRy9pTnVvdm5GTmEyUlU5ZzdKYXV3eThDVGwyZGxrbHlBTEtyCmRWd1BhRnNkWmNKZk13OGVEL0E3aHZXd1RydWM5K29sQmR5dG9wdExGd0crUXQ4MUlSMnRxNjcwdjY0Zkc5UGlPL3l6Y25NY215'));
	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('aVEKaVJNOUhjRUFSd21XbWpnYjNiSFBEY0swUlBPV2xjNHlPbzgwbk9BWHgxN09yZzNiaHpqbFAxdjlteG5oTVVGNmNLb2phd0hoUlV6TgpsTTQ3bmkzbmlBSWk5RzdveU96V1BQTzVzdGQzZXF4NwotLS0tLUVORCBDRVJUSUZJQ0FURS0tLS0tCg=='));
	@fclose($fp);
}
if (!is_file('vendor/cacert.pem')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: vendor/cacert.pem');
	writefile_11();
	if (!is_file('vendor/cacert.pem')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): vendor/cacert.pem');
	} else if (sha1_file('vendor/cacert.pem') != '3c4a17b6c725462993e42152c5ba97645168243a') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): vendor/cacert.pem');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('vendor/cacert.pem', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of vendor/cacert.pem');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('vendor/cacert.pem') !== '3c4a17b6c725462993e42152c5ba97645168243a') {
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/cacert.pem') !== 'cc7062a9e6272e5c0a30817b7136ac34d9484c11') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: vendor/cacert.pem');
			$tmp = pathinfo('vendor/cacert.pem');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('vendor/cacert.pem')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('vendor/cacert.pem', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_11();
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/cacert.pem') !== '3c4a17b6c725462993e42152c5ba97645168243a') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): vendor/cacert.pem');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('vendor/composer/installed.json')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: vendor/composer/installed.json');
	writefile_12();
	if (!is_file('vendor/composer/installed.json')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): vendor/composer/installed.json');
	} else if (sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.json') != '781fafa0ff1b4e9cdb176ad66915d882ee45bea7') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): vendor/composer/installed.json');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('vendor/composer/installed.json', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of vendor/composer/installed.json');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.json') !== '781fafa0ff1b4e9cdb176ad66915d882ee45bea7') {
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.json') !== 'dedeaeae9c0b1f490637c7961a1c887ffbf357d7') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: vendor/composer/installed.json');
			$tmp = pathinfo('vendor/composer/installed.json');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('vendor/composer/installed.json')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('vendor/composer/installed.json', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_12();
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.json') !== '781fafa0ff1b4e9cdb176ad66915d882ee45bea7') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): vendor/composer/installed.json');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('vendor/composer/installed.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: vendor/composer/installed.php');
	writefile_13();
	if (!is_file('vendor/composer/installed.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): vendor/composer/installed.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.php') != '95d7d43061684beaff906e0770fca32bf973afe8') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): vendor/composer/installed.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('vendor/composer/installed.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of vendor/composer/installed.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.php') !== '95d7d43061684beaff906e0770fca32bf973afe8') {
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.php') !== '0386d01a135f89985ca9ac00392a6346cec8c530') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: vendor/composer/installed.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('vendor/composer/installed.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('vendor/composer/installed.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('vendor/composer/installed.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_13();
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.php') !== '95d7d43061684beaff906e0770fca32bf973afe8') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): vendor/composer/installed.php');
		}
	}
}

	} else if (sha1_file('vendor/danielmarschall/vnag/TODO.md') != '80aa406bdd6ff95843428c485a62d87cb0b11cbb') {

	}
} else {

	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('ewogICJuYW1lIjogImpzLXNoYTMiLAogICJ2ZXJzaW9uIjogIjAuOS4zIiwKICAibWFpbiI6IFsic3JjL3NoYTMuanMiXSwKICAiaWdub3JlIjogWwogICAgInNhbXBsZXMiLAogICAgInRlc3RzIgogIF0KfQo='));
	@fclose($fp);
}
if (!is_file('vendor/emn178/js-sha3/bower.json')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: vendor/emn178/js-sha3/bower.json');
	writefile_17();
	if (!is_file('vendor/emn178/js-sha3/bower.json')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): vendor/emn178/js-sha3/bower.json');
	} else if (sha1_file('vendor/emn178/js-sha3/bower.json') != 'e86f9aa00a49d5ee72b0112af99fee3a09ab516d') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): vendor/emn178/js-sha3/bower.json');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('vendor/emn178/js-sha3/bower.json', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of vendor/emn178/js-sha3/bower.json');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('vendor/emn178/js-sha3/bower.json') !== 'e86f9aa00a49d5ee72b0112af99fee3a09ab516d') {
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/emn178/js-sha3/bower.json') !== '290e83cde9e07c4705148a96804b7172469ea444') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: vendor/emn178/js-sha3/bower.json');
			$tmp = pathinfo('vendor/emn178/js-sha3/bower.json');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('vendor/emn178/js-sha3/bower.json')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('vendor/emn178/js-sha3/bower.json', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_17();
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/emn178/js-sha3/bower.json') !== 'e86f9aa00a49d5ee72b0112af99fee3a09ab516d') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): vendor/emn178/js-sha3/bower.json');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('vendor/emn178/js-sha3/build/sha3.min.js')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: vendor/emn178/js-sha3/build/sha3.min.js');
	writefile_18();
	if (!is_file('vendor/emn178/js-sha3/build/sha3.min.js')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): vendor/emn178/js-sha3/build/sha3.min.js');
	} else if (sha1_file('vendor/emn178/js-sha3/build/sha3.min.js') != '3cadb6e89c22387bae8c764228e4653fde77a6ab') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): vendor/emn178/js-sha3/build/sha3.min.js');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('vendor/emn178/js-sha3/build/sha3.min.js', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of vendor/emn178/js-sha3/build/sha3.min.js');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('vendor/emn178/js-sha3/build/sha3.min.js') !== '3cadb6e89c22387bae8c764228e4653fde77a6ab') {
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/emn178/js-sha3/build/sha3.min.js') !== 'de8f421dede51e1b772802d8e05e56cfc13c9d6d') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: vendor/emn178/js-sha3/build/sha3.min.js');
			$tmp = pathinfo('vendor/emn178/js-sha3/build/sha3.min.js');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('vendor/emn178/js-sha3/build/sha3.min.js')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('vendor/emn178/js-sha3/build/sha3.min.js', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_18();
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/emn178/js-sha3/build/sha3.min.js') !== '3cadb6e89c22387bae8c764228e4653fde77a6ab') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): vendor/emn178/js-sha3/build/sha3.min.js');
		}
	}
}

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): vendor/emn178/js-sha3/package-lock.json');
	} else if (sha1_file('vendor/emn178/js-sha3/package-lock.json') != 'dacb4b260c5642eb853daf7b91c3e140266e03bf') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): vendor/emn178/js-sha3/package-lock.json');

			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): vendor/emn178/js-sha3/package-lock.json');

		if (@sha1_file('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Crypt/Common/SymmetricKey.php') !== '494a665724b2232130e589bc5f78a97d1209c233') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Crypt/Common/SymmetricKey.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Crypt/Common/SymmetricKey.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Crypt/Common/SymmetricKey.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Crypt/Common/SymmetricKey.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_24();
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Crypt/Common/SymmetricKey.php') !== 'e66dd000bce1e6f7b77f89b863201a29e15272bc') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Crypt/Common/SymmetricKey.php');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Net/SFTP.php');
	writefile_26();
	if (!is_file('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Net/SFTP.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Net/SFTP.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Net/SFTP.php') != '7789492b33d38665568d406965869ca7c55ec01d') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Net/SFTP.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Net/SFTP.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Net/SFTP.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Net/SFTP.php') !== '7789492b33d38665568d406965869ca7c55ec01d') {
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Net/SFTP.php') !== 'fecfc8a8b03f4dcc0a9546b96f1727ec903e1605') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Net/SFTP.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Net/SFTP.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Net/SFTP.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');

			if (!@copy('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Net/SFTP.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_26();
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Net/SFTP.php') !== '7789492b33d38665568d406965869ca7c55ec01d') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Net/SFTP.php');
